  "description": "Module 10 Chunk 10.5 — Laravel-side observability. Reads from MetricsController (Module 10 Chunk 10.4): horizon_queue_depth, octane_workers_busy, octane_workers_total, pulse_exception_total, slow_queries_total, cache_hit_ratio.",
  "editable": true,
